data.description:
Home and 15 acres approximately 5 miles from American Heartland development site. Property is ideal for both commercial and
residential development. Home is in great shape and would make an ideal STR while acreage allows for a ton of possibilities with
nearly 1000 linear feet of Rd frontage. Centrally located between the existing and new industrial parks.
